configset GLOBAL info_access = VALUE
- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -
Value must be: open, or closed, or list
Default Value: open
Data Type    : enum
Variable Type: access,majordomo
Apply to List: both regular lists and the GLOBAL pseudo-list
= = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = = =

EXAMPLE:
configset GLOBAL info_access = open

(text above is from configshow, Mj2 0.1199902200, extracted 12 Apr 1999)


One of three values: open, list, closed.  Open allows anyone access to this
command.  List allows only list members access, while closed completely
disables the command for everyone.

For a list of all help topics send this one-line message
   help topics
to the server at $MJ
